1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:20,000
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .club, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:00:46,578 --> 00:00:47,578
Zein,

3
00:00:47,704 --> 00:00:48,847
what's this?

4
00:00:48,879 --> 00:00:50,015
What happened to you?

5
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:51,600
It’s Supremo.

6
00:00:51,625 --> 00:00:53,544
Don't make any more offenses.

7
00:00:53,810 --> 00:00:56,271
Next time, you won't be as lucky.

8
00:00:56,296 --> 00:00:57,639
There’s this girl…

9
00:00:57,664 --> 00:00:59,818
I heard from some students
that she's stubborn and rebellious.

10
00:00:59,842 --> 00:01:00,842
Keep an eye on her.

11
00:01:02,138 --> 00:01:03,223
Zein, it's 7:00 p.m.

12
00:01:08,851 --> 00:01:09,746
One!

13
00:01:09,771 --> 00:01:11,064
Two!

14
00:01:12,229 --> 00:01:13,647
Three!

15
00:01:20,646 --> 00:01:22,606
This isn't an ordinary nail.

16
00:01:23,626 --> 00:01:26,379
There's poison and tetanus in it.

17
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:31,284
Let's be grateful that
someone saved you.

18
00:01:31,999 --> 00:01:33,250
You hear that, Zein?

19
00:01:33,590 --> 00:01:34,800
Lesson learned.

20
00:01:35,064 --> 00:01:37,358
It's better to hold your pee in

21
00:01:37,694 --> 00:01:39,237
instead of risking your life.

22
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,805
Sorry, Van.

23
00:01:40,806 --> 00:01:41,890
Look who's apologizing.

24
00:01:41,891 --> 00:01:43,017
Sorry guys.

25
00:01:43,851 --> 00:01:44,851
We're going to be late.

26
00:01:44,852 --> 00:01:45,852
Let’s go?

27
00:01:46,604 --> 00:01:48,856
Are you sure you're not
going to class?

28
00:01:49,273 --> 00:01:50,900
I want to stay by Matt's side.

29
00:01:51,525 --> 00:01:54,612
It's my fault this
happened to him.

30
00:01:54,779 --> 00:01:57,615
Okay, we'll head out.

31
00:02:01,535 --> 00:02:02,535
Zein...

32
00:02:02,703 --> 00:02:04,288
you take care of Matt, okay?

33
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:07,541
Keep your eyes on him!

34
00:02:08,019 --> 00:02:09,124
On Matt!

35
00:02:10,211 --> 00:02:11,295
Alright, I hear you.

36
00:02:31,065 --> 00:02:32,065
Matt...

37
00:02:33,442 --> 00:02:34,944
are you awake?

38
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,488
How are you feeling?

39
00:02:37,863 --> 00:02:39,407
Are you hurt?

40
00:02:40,616 --> 00:02:41,992
Are you okay?

41
00:02:43,744 --> 00:02:44,744
Hey...

42
00:02:44,745 --> 00:02:46,038
Are you hungry?

43
00:02:47,456 --> 00:02:48,456
Thirsty?

44
00:04:52,373 --> 00:04:53,373
Matt...

45
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:56,325
Have you gone insane?

46
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:59,196
Or has the poison reached your brain?

47
00:05:01,156 --> 00:05:02,156
Pepper.

48
00:05:03,325 --> 00:05:05,034
This will purge-

49
00:05:05,035 --> 00:05:06,869
the rest of the poison from my body.

50
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,204
It's so spicy!

51
00:05:08,205 --> 00:05:09,831
It's too hot!

52
00:05:12,376 --> 00:05:13,377
You find that funny?

53
00:05:18,673 --> 00:05:19,299
Hey!

54
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,509
Why did you block it?

55
00:05:20,926 --> 00:05:23,260
If I only knew you we're joking,

56
00:05:23,354 --> 00:05:25,302
I would've punched you harder.

57
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:28,516
You thought the BBG’s nail was lethal?

58
00:05:28,517 --> 00:05:30,352
Wait until you taste this.

59
00:05:32,729 --> 00:05:33,438
Let me see this...

60
00:05:33,438 --> 00:05:34,189
This?

61
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,689
That's nothing!

62
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:37,483
So you're challenging me?

63
00:05:37,484 --> 00:05:38,193
You bet!

64
00:05:38,194 --> 00:05:39,276
- Come on.
- Game?

65
00:05:39,277 --> 00:05:39,736
Let's do it!

66
00:05:39,736 --> 00:05:40,695
- Get ready!
- Try me.

67
00:05:40,695 --> 00:05:41,695
Game.

68
00:05:43,073 --> 00:05:43,907
Give me your best shot.

69
00:05:43,908 --> 00:05:45,200
- Can you handle it?
- Of course!

70
00:05:50,247 --> 00:05:51,832
How dare you!

71
00:06:02,175 --> 00:06:03,176
You know...

72
00:06:03,301 --> 00:06:04,189
Zein...

73
00:06:05,262 --> 00:06:06,262
Zein.

74
00:06:06,388 --> 00:06:07,639
Thank you.

75
00:06:23,905 --> 00:06:24,489
Zein...

76
00:06:24,490 --> 00:06:25,531
I wanted to thank you.

77
00:06:25,532 --> 00:06:27,576
Cause even if it was dangerous out there

78
00:06:27,826 --> 00:06:29,077
you still didn't leave me.

79
00:06:30,745 --> 00:06:33,665
Sorry if you almost got hurt because of me.

80
00:06:34,249 --> 00:06:35,292
Sorry...

81
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,835
Sorry?

82
00:06:38,420 --> 00:06:40,129
It was my fault.

83
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:42,716
What happened to you was my fault.

84
00:06:44,176 --> 00:06:45,635
I just did the right thing.

85
00:06:46,845 --> 00:06:47,929
It was nothing.

86
00:06:50,182 --> 00:06:51,224
You know...

87
00:06:52,434 --> 00:06:54,352
before I fainted.

88
00:06:57,189 --> 00:07:01,109
I saw the guy with the mask.

89
00:07:01,902 --> 00:07:05,280
His mask was red while
the ones chasing us

90
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:07,199
their masks were black.

91
00:07:09,201 --> 00:07:10,827
What if...

92
00:07:12,496 --> 00:07:16,374
their gangs have
designated mask colors?

93
00:07:17,792 --> 00:07:18,793
Right?

94
00:07:18,919 --> 00:07:21,963
If the ones chasing us
were the Black Blood Gang...

95
00:07:22,881 --> 00:07:24,673
I'm certain that the one
who helped us

96
00:07:24,674 --> 00:07:26,301
was part of the
Devil God Warrior.

97
00:07:27,546 --> 00:07:29,798
I saw fear in their eyes...

98
00:07:30,951 --> 00:07:34,205
and their knees were shaking.

99
00:07:35,852 --> 00:07:38,480
They all left in an instant.

100
00:07:40,899 --> 00:07:43,235
That guy must not be
an ordinary member.

101
00:07:45,111 --> 00:07:46,404
I think...

102
00:07:48,281 --> 00:07:50,492
he must be Raze Silvenia.

103
00:07:50,825 --> 00:07:53,662
The leader of the
Devil God Warrior.

104
00:07:54,871 --> 00:07:56,873
But why would he help us?

105
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,543
I don't know either, Zein.

106
00:07:59,544 --> 00:08:01,253
I ask myself that question too.

107
00:08:12,347 --> 00:08:14,140
When we were running
away from them...

108
00:08:14,933 --> 00:08:17,477
I already noticed
something watching us.

109
00:08:17,936 --> 00:08:19,854
If he's from the
Black Blood Gang,

110
00:08:20,438 --> 00:08:22,607
he would've killed us already.

111
00:08:24,859 --> 00:08:27,070
Is it possible that
Raze was there?

112
00:08:28,196 --> 00:08:31,157
Was the Devil God Warrior
out there that night?

113
00:08:32,951 --> 00:08:33,493
It's possible.

114
00:08:33,494 --> 00:08:35,036
But why?

115
00:08:48,341 --> 00:08:50,802
We won't find answers
to our questions.

116
00:08:51,177 --> 00:08:52,219
For now,

117
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:55,640
what we can do is rest.

118
00:08:56,641 --> 00:08:58,310
And try to catch up
on our classes.

119
00:09:01,605 --> 00:09:03,565
Let's show everyone
in Hell University

120
00:09:04,065 --> 00:09:06,401
that they don't scare us.

121
00:09:13,575 --> 00:09:15,242
We're going to be late!

122
00:09:15,243 --> 00:09:16,453
What time is it?

123
00:09:16,828 --> 00:09:19,039
I want to go to class.

124
00:09:19,289 --> 00:09:20,289
Let's go?

125
00:09:22,042 --> 00:09:23,500
We're already late.
Come on!

126
00:09:23,501 --> 00:09:25,086
Just a minute, it still hurts.

127
00:09:25,545 --> 00:09:26,545
Can you handle yourself?

128
00:09:31,718 --> 00:09:33,803
My lips are still pale, Zein.

129
00:09:36,389 --> 00:09:37,389
Miss...

130
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,600
are you okay?

131
00:09:38,933 --> 00:09:40,101
Are you alright?

132
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,729
What happened?

133
00:09:46,103 --> 00:09:47,188
No, please!

134
00:09:59,454 --> 00:10:00,872
Good morning class.

135
00:10:01,623 --> 00:10:03,291
Before anything else...

136
00:10:03,583 --> 00:10:05,710
I have a big announcement!

137
00:10:05,877 --> 00:10:07,086
Well, it's been a while

138
00:10:07,087 --> 00:10:08,629
since we've had this event

139
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:11,216
or any event for that matter.

140
00:10:11,591 --> 00:10:12,884
That is why

141
00:10:13,051 --> 00:10:15,219
I am so happy to announce

142
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:17,764
on behalf of the
Hell U administration

143
00:10:17,972 --> 00:10:20,892
that we will be having another

144
00:10:22,435 --> 00:10:24,104
acquaintance party!

145
00:10:31,403 --> 00:10:34,614
I know. I'm sure you're all excited.

146
00:10:34,781 --> 00:10:35,906
That's why we hope

147
00:10:35,907 --> 00:10:37,950
that you keep that enthusiasm

148
00:10:37,951 --> 00:10:40,577
as we roll out details
in the incoming days.

149
00:10:40,578 --> 00:10:41,996
Teacher Kath?

150
00:10:43,915 --> 00:10:45,166
Yes, Celine?

151
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:49,379
I think...

152
00:10:49,883 --> 00:10:54,387
this isn't the right time to celebrate.

153
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:59,848
Especially from the deaths
these past few weeks...

154
00:11:00,432 --> 00:11:03,226
It is unfortunately out
of my hands, Celine.

155
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:06,271
Madam Violet has
made her decision.

156
00:11:06,646 --> 00:11:08,480
And things are already moving

157
00:11:08,481 --> 00:11:10,232
to have it done by this Friday.

158
00:11:10,233 --> 00:11:11,233
But...

159
00:11:11,568 --> 00:11:14,362
don't you also have
the power to stop the event?

160
00:11:14,863 --> 00:11:16,613
Maybe you could reason
with Madam Violet-

161
00:11:16,614 --> 00:11:17,871
Enough, Celine!

162
00:11:18,658 --> 00:11:19,826
Like I said...

163
00:11:20,076 --> 00:11:23,371
more details will be rolled
over the coming days.

164
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:27,876
Now, we still have class.

165
00:11:28,251 --> 00:11:29,251
Let's start!

166
00:11:29,627 --> 00:11:31,837
So last time if you remember,

167
00:11:31,939 --> 00:11:34,910
we talked about energy, right?

168
00:11:35,425 --> 00:11:37,886
Potential and kinetic energy.

169
00:11:38,553 --> 00:11:40,221
Acquaintance party?

170
00:11:40,896 --> 00:11:42,522
What are they planning to do?

171
00:11:43,223 --> 00:11:44,325
Whatever they're planning on

172
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:47,278
and whoever started this...

173
00:11:47,895 --> 00:11:50,300
my friends and I aren't pushovers.

174
00:11:51,057 --> 00:11:52,892
We're not afraid of you...

175
00:11:53,651 --> 00:11:54,694
The admin,

176
00:11:55,278 --> 00:11:56,696
the Black Blood Gang,

177
00:11:57,363 --> 00:11:59,032
or the Devil God Warrior.

178
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:01,869
They should be the
ones afraid of us.

179
00:12:40,351 --> 00:12:41,728
Excuse me, sir?

180
00:12:42,826 --> 00:12:43,660
Boss...

181
00:12:43,661 --> 00:12:45,912
Is this your only branch?
Or are there others?

182
00:12:46,788 --> 00:12:47,747
Don't be rude!

183
00:12:47,748 --> 00:12:49,081
Thank you!

184
00:12:49,082 --> 00:12:50,082
Thank you.

185
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:55,420
Matt...

186
00:12:55,463 --> 00:12:57,173
you sure you're okay?

187
00:12:57,549 --> 00:12:59,007
Don't you need to rest more?

188
00:12:59,108 --> 00:13:00,151
I'm okay.

189
00:13:00,253 --> 00:13:03,207
The pepper took care
of the poison.

190
00:13:04,389 --> 00:13:06,098
Eat another one so you're sure.

191
00:13:06,099 --> 00:13:07,558
Purge it out of you.

192
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:08,685
What?

193
00:13:09,379 --> 00:13:10,103
You know what...

194
00:13:10,104 --> 00:13:12,188
while you're busy with
your inside jokes

195
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,982
Dave and Jerome have
been looking for ways

196
00:13:14,983 --> 00:13:16,693
to escape this place.

197
00:13:16,901 --> 00:13:18,987
Because of what happened
with you both last night...

198
00:13:19,237 --> 00:13:19,988
my God!

199
00:13:19,989 --> 00:13:22,490
We need to act faster.

200
00:13:22,824 --> 00:13:24,742
We tried to find the road
that led us here...

201
00:13:26,244 --> 00:13:28,120
but it's so strange

202
00:13:28,121 --> 00:13:29,873
it seems like the roads
have changed.

203
00:13:30,915 --> 00:13:32,625
Any road we walk on...

204
00:13:33,293 --> 00:13:34,919
it leads us to nowhere.

205
00:13:35,587 --> 00:13:36,963
What are we going to do?

206
00:13:37,755 --> 00:13:39,966
We entered this
place unknowingly...

207
00:13:40,981 --> 00:13:43,340
We don't know it's history

208
00:13:43,979 --> 00:13:45,648
or who runs this place.

209
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:47,599
We need information

210
00:13:48,231 --> 00:13:49,482
so we can fight back

211
00:13:50,170 --> 00:13:51,463
and escape.

212
00:13:51,936 --> 00:13:53,897
If we need to kill

213
00:13:54,355 --> 00:13:55,732
to escape, so be it!

214
00:13:57,525 --> 00:13:59,568
We need to strike first

215
00:13:59,569 --> 00:14:01,446
to get leverage.

216
00:14:02,619 --> 00:14:04,705
From the tone of that voice of yours...

217
00:14:04,908 --> 00:14:06,659
I'm sure you have a plan.

218
00:14:06,868 --> 00:14:07,911
Celine.

219
00:14:08,369 --> 00:14:09,661
She knows something.

220
00:14:09,662 --> 00:14:11,456
I thought of the same thing...

221
00:14:11,915 --> 00:14:13,958
but she's wary of us.

222
00:14:14,558 --> 00:14:16,227
It's like she's afraid of us.

223
00:14:16,384 --> 00:14:17,469
I'll handle that.

224
00:14:18,504 --> 00:14:21,466
Maybe she has information
about the gangs here too...

225
00:14:21,722 --> 00:14:24,141
We need to find a way
to deal with those gangs.

226
00:14:24,512 --> 00:14:25,512
No!

227
00:14:26,804 --> 00:14:27,846
I don't think it's the right decision

228
00:14:27,847 --> 00:14:29,390
to meddle with the gangs.

229
00:14:30,254 --> 00:14:31,893
Why are you overreacting?

230
00:14:33,561 --> 00:14:34,771
It's not like that.

231
00:14:35,688 --> 00:14:37,398
But after what happened
last night...

232
00:14:37,857 --> 00:14:39,066
maybe it's better to investigate

233
00:14:39,067 --> 00:14:40,526
about the University itself?

234
00:14:41,861 --> 00:14:43,320
If the gangs find out that

235
00:14:43,321 --> 00:14:45,572
we're asking too many
questions about them...

236
00:14:45,573 --> 00:14:47,200
we can get hurt.

237
00:14:47,951 --> 00:14:48,951
Dave.

238
00:14:49,619 --> 00:14:52,413
If we know the
history of this place

239
00:14:53,057 --> 00:14:55,266
everything will align.

240
00:14:55,432 --> 00:14:58,227
The substantial part
of HU's history

241
00:14:58,275 --> 00:14:59,610
are the gangs.

242
00:14:59,963 --> 00:15:02,131
It doesn't matter which
one we prod first.

243
00:15:03,091 --> 00:15:05,009
We need information to fight this battle.

244
00:15:05,343 --> 00:15:07,469
That's why we need
to find answers.

245
00:15:07,672 --> 00:15:09,007
You're right.

246
00:15:09,305 --> 00:15:13,309
Let's try to find information
our own way.

247
00:15:14,686 --> 00:15:15,937
Now's the time.

248
00:15:16,229 --> 00:15:18,106
Let's realign later.

249
00:15:22,819 --> 00:15:23,820
Celine!

250
00:15:25,238 --> 00:15:26,405
Come on, let's go.

251
00:15:26,406 --> 00:15:27,573
Hold on.

252
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,118
I won't hurt you.

253
00:15:31,077 --> 00:15:32,077
I just want to talk.

254
00:15:33,371 --> 00:15:34,955
Stay away from us.

255
00:15:34,956 --> 00:15:36,206
We don't want you to get hurt.

256
00:15:36,207 --> 00:15:37,583
It's too late for that.

257
00:15:37,625 --> 00:15:39,711
We've been marked since
we entered this place.

258
00:15:40,878 --> 00:15:42,046
Please...

259
00:15:42,213 --> 00:15:43,464
we need your help.

260
00:15:44,716 --> 00:15:45,883
Celine...

261
00:15:47,093 --> 00:15:48,177
It's okay.

262
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:57,271
Not here.

263
00:16:43,038 --> 00:16:44,664
I need to ask you this, Zein.

264
00:16:50,433 --> 00:16:51,768
Are you ready...

265
00:16:53,257 --> 00:16:55,343
to trade your life-

266
00:16:56,204 --> 00:16:58,331
for this information?

267
00:17:01,302 --> 00:17:03,387
Tell me everything you know.

268
00:17:04,385 --> 00:17:05,970
You're brave now, Zein.

269
00:17:06,422 --> 00:17:07,715
You are brave.

270
00:17:08,424 --> 00:17:09,717
You are brave...

271
00:17:11,052 --> 00:17:12,220
But...

272
00:17:13,346 --> 00:17:14,931
they used to be brave like you.

273
00:17:16,265 --> 00:17:17,683
The previous newbies.

274
00:17:19,894 --> 00:17:22,396
They were more curious than brave.

275
00:17:24,107 --> 00:17:25,525
Remember.

276
00:17:27,819 --> 00:17:31,239
It's easy to ask questions.

277
00:17:33,552 --> 00:17:37,014
But it's difficult to handle
the burden of the truth.

278
00:17:39,948 --> 00:17:41,074
Try me.

279
00:18:10,404 --> 00:18:13,991
Hell University was once called-

280
00:18:14,189 --> 00:18:17,484
“Philippine High University.”

281
00:18:18,286 --> 00:18:20,289
Only the children of the wealthy

282
00:18:20,314 --> 00:18:23,539
and powerful can enter this school.

283
00:18:26,043 --> 00:18:27,043
But...

284
00:18:27,068 --> 00:18:28,234
everything changed.

285
00:18:28,446 --> 00:18:35,850
When the founder, Dr. Quizon,
lost his mind.

286
00:18:36,234 --> 00:18:38,499
He was a well known scientist.

287
00:18:39,868 --> 00:18:41,619
But he used this school's
high tuition fees

288
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:45,500
to fund his research.

289
00:18:46,583 --> 00:18:49,211
He slowly lost his mind

290
00:18:49,698 --> 00:18:54,369
and used the students within
the university in his obsession.

291
00:18:57,595 --> 00:19:00,079
A formula-

292
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:03,518
who can revive the dead.

293
00:19:06,646 --> 00:19:08,023
Immortality

294
00:19:09,357 --> 00:19:10,772
and revival.

295
00:19:12,986 --> 00:19:14,279
One day.

296
00:19:14,571 --> 00:19:16,489
Everybody was blindsided.

297
00:19:16,865 --> 00:19:18,985
All the exits have been blocked.
There was no way out.

298
00:19:19,743 --> 00:19:21,137
The admins managed to find a way

299
00:19:21,162 --> 00:19:25,319
to hide the whole university
from the whole country.

300
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:28,436
Nobody had the power to do
anything, even the parents.

301
00:19:29,669 --> 00:19:34,163
I was one of the first students
who got trapped in this hellhole.

302
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:37,301
We don't know how

303
00:19:38,086 --> 00:19:42,975
but it's like we've been sealed
inside a hidden pocket universe.

304
00:19:45,812 --> 00:19:49,566
They used all of us
in his experiments.

305
00:19:50,244 --> 00:19:52,999
The ones who died first
were the lucky ones.

306
00:19:53,610 --> 00:19:55,278
It was chaos.

307
00:19:55,695 --> 00:19:57,213
Some tried to fight back,

308
00:19:57,238 --> 00:19:58,573
some rebelled.

309
00:19:59,205 --> 00:20:03,859
But most turned on each other to release
their rage. It didn't take long before.

310
00:20:04,537 --> 00:20:09,184
PHU turned into Hell U.

311
00:20:09,209 --> 00:20:11,419
From the chaos and bloodshed

312
00:20:11,711 --> 00:20:14,214
many gangs were formed.

313
00:20:14,631 --> 00:20:17,883
You already know the two
most powerful gangs here.

314
00:20:19,427 --> 00:20:23,681
The Black Blood Gang
and The Devil God Warrior.

315
00:20:24,114 --> 00:20:26,624
Dr. Quizon completed the formula

316
00:20:27,352 --> 00:20:31,758
but he died before he
could use it for himself.

317
00:20:33,525 --> 00:20:35,377
There were rumors saying that

318
00:20:35,402 --> 00:20:39,923
a student got his hands
on the formula.

319
00:20:39,948 --> 00:20:42,909
That student is still in Hell U.

320
00:20:43,743 --> 00:20:47,705
That's why they locked this
place from the world.

321
00:20:48,973 --> 00:20:54,389
The officals and the forces outside
are still looking for that student

322
00:20:54,414 --> 00:20:58,014
because they're desperate to
get a hold of that formula.

323
00:21:01,114 --> 00:21:02,114
Zein,

324
00:21:03,491 --> 00:21:05,348
that's Hell U's secret.

325
00:21:06,933 --> 00:21:10,103
That's why no one is allowed to leave.

326
00:21:10,937 --> 00:21:13,940
They believe that student
is still here.

327
00:21:14,649 --> 00:21:16,234
It could be anyone.

328
00:21:21,781 --> 00:21:23,908
That person's life is in danger.

329
00:21:27,023 --> 00:21:28,108
I’m sure

330
00:21:28,588 --> 00:21:30,131
it'll only take a while

331
00:21:30,999 --> 00:21:33,501
before the officials find
out who that student is.

332
00:21:35,518 --> 00:21:37,645
You know what I'm more afraid of?

333
00:21:38,965 --> 00:21:40,585
The formula getting-

334
00:21:42,385 --> 00:21:44,345
into the hands of the wrong people.

335
00:21:47,072 --> 00:21:49,157
And using it for evil.

336
00:22:08,703 --> 00:22:11,206
Now you know the secret of Hell U.

337
00:22:12,290 --> 00:22:14,501
You will never get to leave.

338
00:22:16,468 --> 00:22:18,053
You will die here.

339
00:22:20,340 --> 00:22:23,009
Do you know the student
who has the formula?

340
00:22:24,761 --> 00:22:26,095
If you do know...

341
00:22:27,388 --> 00:22:28,932
it's time to take extra precautions.

342
00:22:29,891 --> 00:22:31,601
Because it's hard to get
out of this-

343
00:22:32,602 --> 00:22:34,312
once you've become involved.

344
00:22:34,896 --> 00:22:36,231
You'll get involved, Zein.

345
00:22:37,106 --> 00:22:38,525
You'll get involved.

346
00:23:06,052 --> 00:23:09,389
I talk big about how
information is our weapon.

347
00:23:12,109 --> 00:23:13,909
What am I supposed
to do with Celine’s story?

348
00:23:16,187 --> 00:23:18,731
Should I tell the others what I found out?

349
00:23:22,318 --> 00:23:24,008
They might just get dragged into this.

350
00:23:29,003 --> 00:23:30,772
But if I keep quiet...

351
00:23:34,998 --> 00:23:37,000
Did you like Celine's story?

352
00:23:38,209 --> 00:23:40,128
You don't know how
to listen, do you?

353
00:23:41,421 --> 00:23:43,047
I know everything.

354
00:23:44,424 --> 00:23:45,425
Everything?

355
00:23:46,384 --> 00:23:47,635
Don't be so sure.

356
00:23:49,894 --> 00:23:51,938
That's only half of the story.

357
00:23:52,098 --> 00:23:53,850
You don't know everything yet, Zein.

358
00:23:54,399 --> 00:23:57,861
But you went ahead and
made yourself a target anyway.

359
00:23:58,313 --> 00:23:59,689
Brace yourself.

360
00:24:00,204 --> 00:24:02,165
You're going to die soon.

361
00:24:26,299 --> 00:24:27,383
What happened?

362
00:24:28,176 --> 00:24:29,552
Are you okay?

363
00:24:33,181 --> 00:24:35,475
It's Ms. Leonora, the librarian.

364
00:24:35,808 --> 00:24:37,101
She tried to scare us off.

365
00:24:39,690 --> 00:24:41,064
What did she say?

366
00:24:43,024 --> 00:24:46,292
She said that the cost of the
information we're looking for

367
00:24:46,690 --> 00:24:49,346
is being stuck here
in HU permanently.

368
00:24:51,669 --> 00:24:55,005
That's what the students
we asked said too.

369
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,964
It was creepy.

370
00:24:58,212 --> 00:24:59,922
She kept on saying:

371
00:25:00,668 --> 00:25:02,044
There's a cost

372
00:25:04,711 --> 00:25:06,254
in the information
you're looking for.

373
00:25:19,227 --> 00:25:20,583
Leave this place!

374
00:25:21,521 --> 00:25:23,317
She didn't answer our question

375
00:25:23,564 --> 00:25:26,483
but she said something about
being able to leave this place.

376
00:25:26,984 --> 00:25:29,075
Vanessa and I waited for
all of us to be complete

377
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:31,144
before we shared this information.

378
00:25:33,074 --> 00:25:35,243
What is it? She showed
you the way out?

379
00:25:37,328 --> 00:25:40,331
We need to get up
the ranks in HU.

380
00:25:42,019 --> 00:25:43,019
Rank?

381
00:25:43,044 --> 00:25:44,212
What rank?

382
00:25:45,138 --> 00:25:47,487
You mean the classroom rankings?

383
00:25:48,548 --> 00:25:50,216
Top achievers?

384
00:25:50,758 --> 00:25:52,593
Not just in the classroom...

385
00:25:53,177 --> 00:25:56,055
The overall HU rankings.

386
00:25:57,974 --> 00:25:58,974
This is the list.

387
00:25:59,517 --> 00:26:02,603
As of now, Raze Silvenia is
in the top of the ranks.

388
00:26:02,895 --> 00:26:03,896
Give me that.

389
00:26:04,856 --> 00:26:06,524
Not that, the cookies!

390
00:26:07,025 --> 00:26:08,484
Jerome, you're so annoying.

391
00:26:11,112 --> 00:26:12,739
Nazzer Lumia.

392
00:26:14,574 --> 00:26:16,701
I think he's the leader of
the Black Blood Gang.

393
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,595
Both the leaders

394
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:22,080
of the two most powerful gangs

395
00:26:22,081 --> 00:26:23,541
are in the top of the ranks.

396
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:25,752
I don't think that's a coincidence.

397
00:26:27,003 --> 00:26:28,463
It could be a lead.

398
00:26:29,505 --> 00:26:30,757
I think you're right!

399
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:33,009
But it's clear to me

400
00:26:33,259 --> 00:26:36,262
that if we ask more
information about Hell University,

401
00:26:36,429 --> 00:26:38,264
we'll be in more danger
that we already are.

402
00:26:38,556 --> 00:26:42,477
Information about this school,
the gangs...

403
00:26:45,438 --> 00:26:46,522
But this...

404
00:26:47,148 --> 00:26:48,024
I'm sure if we try to get into the ranks

405
00:26:48,025 --> 00:26:49,650
we won't be hurt.

406
00:26:49,984 --> 00:26:51,652
We just need to be good students.

407
00:26:52,445 --> 00:26:55,656
We need to work hard to
get into the top ten rank.

408
00:26:56,532 --> 00:26:58,326
We'll make it out alive.

409
00:27:00,203 --> 00:27:01,370
How about you, Zein?

410
00:27:01,621 --> 00:27:03,289
Did you find any answers?

411
00:27:05,708 --> 00:27:09,128
What did Celine tell you?

412
00:27:13,007 --> 00:27:15,813
I cannot tell them what I found out.

413
00:27:49,752 --> 00:27:53,172
Give me that! Hey!

414
00:28:52,634 --> 00:28:54,334
That's his third warning.

415
00:28:54,503 --> 00:28:55,295
Really?

416
00:28:55,401 --> 00:28:56,736
That's the last warning.

417
00:28:56,861 --> 00:28:59,071
They might bring him to
the Dark Hell Jail.

418
00:29:11,792 --> 00:29:13,169
As you can see

419
00:29:13,836 --> 00:29:16,212
the festival committee is
working so hard

420
00:29:16,213 --> 00:29:18,921
to finish the decorations
for this Friday's event.

421
00:29:21,452 --> 00:29:23,120
Despite the very tight schedule,

422
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:24,554
they're doing everything they can

423
00:29:24,555 --> 00:29:26,599
to make it as smooth as possible.

424
00:29:26,974 --> 00:29:29,268
I'm sure you've guessed from the decor

425
00:29:29,894 --> 00:29:31,718
but I'm going to make it official.

426
00:29:32,162 --> 00:29:34,190
That this Friday's event

427
00:29:34,611 --> 00:29:38,185
is going to be a masquerade.

428
00:29:43,787 --> 00:29:46,832
Masks are mandatory.

429
00:29:47,554 --> 00:29:50,557
While we encourage creativity

430
00:29:51,089 --> 00:29:53,383
and freedom of expression,

431
00:29:54,611 --> 00:29:58,824
we highly prohibit the use of two colors.

432
00:30:00,001 --> 00:30:02,209
Red and black.

433
00:30:04,006 --> 00:30:06,717
These colors are exclusive

434
00:30:07,094 --> 00:30:12,318
for the Devil God Warrior and
the Black Blood Gang.

435
00:30:13,312 --> 00:30:16,052
Non members cannot
use these colors.

436
00:30:16,315 --> 00:30:20,403
To ensure compliance, we're gonna
send your outfits to your dorm.

437
00:30:20,778 --> 00:30:23,698
Feel free to make your masks.

438
00:30:24,205 --> 00:30:28,042
We'll call next Friday,
Free Bloody Night.

439
00:30:28,972 --> 00:30:32,623
Where killing is prohibited.

440
00:30:35,251 --> 00:30:38,123
Breaking this rule

441
00:30:39,505 --> 00:30:43,873
is punishable by death.

442
00:30:54,645 --> 00:30:58,398
Now, I'd like to call on
Supreme Student President.

443
00:30:58,399 --> 00:31:01,381
Ace Craige for more announcements.

444
00:31:13,039 --> 00:31:15,357
Thank you, Madam Violet.

445
00:31:16,852 --> 00:31:18,728
Some pressing concerns will

446
00:31:18,753 --> 00:31:22,214
prevent me from attending
this Friday's festivities.

447
00:31:23,507 --> 00:31:27,344
In short, I won't be there.

448
00:31:29,013 --> 00:31:30,389
Why is he not attending?

449
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,850
But beware...

450
00:31:35,186 --> 00:31:36,437
I will be watching you.

451
00:32:12,348 --> 00:32:16,602
Wanted: Supreme Student
Government Secretary.

452
00:32:26,794 --> 00:32:29,922
Aren’t you going to
step out of my way?

453
00:32:33,668 --> 00:32:34,669
Should I?

454
00:32:35,162 --> 00:32:38,749
I'm the Supreme Student
Government Secretary here.

455
00:32:39,079 --> 00:32:42,166
Miss... I don't care who you are.

456
00:32:45,214 --> 00:32:47,091
Former secretary.

457
00:32:47,675 --> 00:32:48,843
Can't you read?

458
00:32:49,426 --> 00:32:51,178
Or should I read it for you?

459
00:32:51,846 --> 00:32:53,764
That's just a paper.

460
00:32:54,265 --> 00:32:56,475
A mistake, obviously!

461
00:32:56,778 --> 00:32:59,114
I haven't stepped down
from my position!

462
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,981
Stop complaining.

463
00:33:02,833 --> 00:33:04,750
You've been kicked
out of your position.

464
00:33:04,775 --> 00:33:05,901
Miss...

465
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:07,211
Fritzy.

466
00:33:07,319 --> 00:33:09,071
I don't care about your name.

467
00:33:09,822 --> 00:33:11,782
Maybe you're just not qualified.

468
00:33:14,201 --> 00:33:15,631
What are you doing?

469
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:23,394
How dare you!

470
00:33:23,419 --> 00:33:24,461
Stop them!

471
00:33:27,214 --> 00:33:29,175
Stop them!

472
00:33:47,324 --> 00:33:49,409
What the fuck is wrong with you?

473
00:33:50,321 --> 00:33:52,406
You don’t have the right to hurt

474
00:33:52,615 --> 00:33:55,117
the Supreme Student Secretary!

475
00:33:55,534 --> 00:33:59,622
An insult to one of us
is an insult to all of us!

476
00:34:00,079 --> 00:34:02,099
Do I look like I care?

477
00:34:02,733 --> 00:34:04,902
Mark my words...

478
00:34:05,419 --> 00:34:10,299
I will use eveything in
my power to crush you.

479
00:34:10,674 --> 00:34:12,343
You won't be able to
escape my grudge.

480
00:34:13,135 --> 00:34:15,638
You can use all the power you have

481
00:34:16,263 --> 00:34:19,891
but it doesn't change the fact
that Fritzy is a bitch

482
00:34:19,892 --> 00:34:21,936
and you are an asshole.

483
00:34:41,455 --> 00:34:42,498
If you hit her...

484
00:34:42,957 --> 00:34:43,791
that would've been a third
warning for you

485
00:34:43,792 --> 00:34:45,376
and the former secretary

486
00:34:45,668 --> 00:34:48,128
Mr. President, my
sincerest apologies.

487
00:34:50,214 --> 00:34:51,757
I want this room cleared!

488
00:34:52,675 --> 00:34:54,009
On my command!

489
00:34:54,551 --> 00:34:55,551
One.

490
00:34:56,011 --> 00:34:57,971
President, if you would
let me explain

491
00:34:58,089 --> 00:35:00,049
it isn't Fritzy's fault.

492
00:35:00,099 --> 00:35:01,766
It was this good for nothing.

493
00:35:01,767 --> 00:35:02,726
It's this bitch who started-

494
00:35:02,727 --> 00:35:03,894
Two.

495
00:35:21,715 --> 00:35:23,091
Kill me now.

496
00:35:23,514 --> 00:35:25,057
Not yet, Ms. Shion.

497
00:35:25,167 --> 00:35:27,701
You need to heal before
you face your punishment, okay?

498
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:49,600
Cause you're the type of bitch
that’s qualified to be my secretary.

499
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:52,092
So you need to be
treated immediately.

500
00:35:52,985 --> 00:35:54,451
Kill me now.

501
00:36:06,457 --> 00:36:07,458
Nurse Cha!

502
00:36:08,459 --> 00:36:09,543
Nurse Cha!

503
00:36:10,919 --> 00:36:11,919
Supremo...

504
00:36:12,921 --> 00:36:15,299
I don't want to see any
scars on her forehead.

505
00:36:17,509 --> 00:36:18,635
Let me check on her.

506
00:36:33,442 --> 00:36:35,944
I can't guarantee you
that it won't leave a scar.

507
00:36:37,279 --> 00:36:39,490
Well, you wouldn't let that
happen to my secretary.

508
00:36:40,199 --> 00:36:41,658
Right, Nurse Cha?

509
00:36:44,495 --> 00:36:45,537
Patch her up.

510
00:36:45,746 --> 00:36:46,746
Now.

511
00:36:47,206 --> 00:36:48,499
Yes, Supremo.

512
00:36:49,792 --> 00:36:53,316
Hey, I didn't agree
to that position yet.

513
00:37:18,821 --> 00:37:20,238
What happened to Zein?

514
00:37:20,239 --> 00:37:21,365
What happened to her?

515
00:37:25,536 --> 00:37:26,824
Oh my God, Zein!

516
00:37:27,246 --> 00:37:28,704
What did you get
yourself into this time

517
00:37:28,705 --> 00:37:31,208
that the SSG President
did that to you?

518
00:37:32,501 --> 00:37:34,097
President?

519
00:37:35,943 --> 00:37:37,695
The whole school's been
talking about it.

520
00:37:38,298 --> 00:37:40,759
Others said that the
President did this to you.

521
00:37:40,926 --> 00:37:42,469
A lot of people saw it, Zein.

522
00:37:45,431 --> 00:37:47,349
They're just making up stories.

523
00:37:47,850 --> 00:37:49,768
Who would you believe?

524
00:37:50,185 --> 00:37:51,228
Me?

525
00:37:51,353 --> 00:37:52,354
Or other people?

526
00:38:03,857 --> 00:38:05,942
Onel was the one who pushed me

527
00:38:06,983 --> 00:38:09,383
because I got into a fight with
his bitch of a girlfriend.

528
00:38:10,122 --> 00:38:12,958
I knew it! You started
something again.

529
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:16,628
Am I just going to let the queen
bee wannabees disrespect me?

530
00:38:16,653 --> 00:38:19,072
You have a point, we
hate those kind of girls.

531
00:38:21,489 --> 00:38:22,531
She started it...

532
00:38:23,177 --> 00:38:24,344
I finished it.

533
00:38:25,220 --> 00:38:28,891
Isn't the plan to stay
away from trouble?

534
00:38:29,016 --> 00:38:31,059
I guess they didn't
get the memo.

535
00:38:32,728 --> 00:38:34,146
At least you're okay.

536
00:38:34,943 --> 00:38:35,943
I'm okay.

537
00:38:36,890 --> 00:38:39,934
I didn't faint. I just fell asleep.

538
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:46,658
If the President didn't bring me here

539
00:38:46,783 --> 00:38:48,535
it could've been a lot worse.

540
00:38:55,292 --> 00:38:56,668
That made me hungry.

541
00:38:57,711 --> 00:38:59,671
Do you guys have snacks?

542
00:39:00,547 --> 00:39:02,216
I knew it.

543
00:39:07,304 --> 00:39:08,628
He's so sweet.

544
00:39:09,938 --> 00:39:11,898
It's a little cold.

545
00:39:12,843 --> 00:39:13,843
Thanks.

546
00:39:16,028 --> 00:39:17,363
Ms. Zein Shion...

547
00:39:26,740 --> 00:39:27,740
What do you want?

548
00:39:27,798 --> 00:39:29,383
Do you want to fight again?

549
00:39:34,124 --> 00:39:35,124
Ms. Shion.

550
00:39:38,252 --> 00:39:39,378
What's happening?

551
00:39:40,546 --> 00:39:41,880
Ms. Zein Shion.

552
00:39:42,464 --> 00:39:45,342
I humbly ask for your forgiveness.

553
00:39:45,676 --> 00:39:47,480
I lost my mind for a bit.

554
00:39:48,136 --> 00:39:49,846
I didn't know what I was doing.

555
00:39:52,140 --> 00:39:53,644
Please forgive me.

556
00:39:54,434 --> 00:39:55,519
Oh my God.

557
00:39:58,021 --> 00:40:00,315
Public apology speed run?

558
00:40:02,276 --> 00:40:03,800
Please forgive me.

559
00:40:05,487 --> 00:40:06,589
Ms. Shion...

560
00:40:08,323 --> 00:40:09,783
Please.

561
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:13,661
Ms. Shion, please!

562
00:40:13,976 --> 00:40:15,519
Forgive me!

563
00:40:16,299 --> 00:40:18,009
I'm not ready to die!

564
00:40:22,904 --> 00:40:23,904
Fine.

565
00:40:24,373 --> 00:40:25,666
Whatever.

566
00:40:26,124 --> 00:40:28,126
Stand up and leave.

567
00:40:29,469 --> 00:40:30,804
I want to eat in peace.

568
00:40:35,225 --> 00:40:36,435
Thank you...

569
00:40:37,281 --> 00:40:38,658
Thank you, Ms. Shion.

570
00:40:40,070 --> 00:40:41,321
Thank you.

571
00:40:44,325 --> 00:40:45,868
Let's go! Let's go!

572
00:40:53,011 --> 00:40:55,220
And why is the SSG Vice President

573
00:40:55,245 --> 00:40:57,683
begging for your forgiveness?

574
00:41:00,834 --> 00:41:02,210
Let's not think about it.

575
00:41:02,336 --> 00:41:03,879
I'm too hungry for that.

576
00:41:16,308 --> 00:41:17,434
Yum.

577
00:41:52,052 --> 00:41:55,430
Hi, good evening, how are
you? Take a mask please.

578
00:43:02,956 --> 00:43:06,418
This place finally feels
like a normal school.

579
00:43:06,543 --> 00:43:08,628
I think that's their intention

580
00:43:09,421 --> 00:43:12,048
to distract us from what's happening.

581
00:43:12,257 --> 00:43:14,176
So it's easier to control us.

582
00:43:14,426 --> 00:43:17,511
But it's not so bad to
have a little fun, right?

583
00:43:17,512 --> 00:43:18,721
You're right.

584
00:43:18,722 --> 00:43:19,722
Yeah, but don't forget

585
00:43:19,723 --> 00:43:23,435
we still have to take precautions.

586
00:43:23,690 --> 00:43:24,825
Let’s stay here.

587
00:43:27,731 --> 00:43:29,291
I didn't it'll be a full house tonight.

588
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:30,900
Girls...

589
00:43:30,939 --> 00:43:32,065
stay close.

590
00:43:32,248 --> 00:43:33,624
Stay by our sides, okay?

591
00:43:36,147 --> 00:43:38,066
Even if it's Free Bloody Night

592
00:43:38,909 --> 00:43:41,203
we still can't trust them.

593
00:43:42,871 --> 00:43:45,207
Aw, our heroes.

594
00:43:45,506 --> 00:43:48,092
I'm still unsure why
Supremo isn't coming...

595
00:43:51,296 --> 00:43:52,839
What's with the commotion?

596
00:43:54,758 --> 00:43:56,051
What's up everyone!

597
00:44:01,284 --> 00:44:02,577
It's red hair!

598
00:44:23,056 --> 00:44:24,638
Is that Raze?

599
00:44:27,503 --> 00:44:28,504
Okay...

600
00:44:28,529 --> 00:44:29,863
that ruined the mood.

601
00:44:29,888 --> 00:44:31,806
So this is what their usual
parties look like?

602
00:44:32,737 --> 00:44:34,322
What more if it's a prom.

603
00:44:35,730 --> 00:44:38,232
I hope we get to leave
before we see that.

604
00:44:38,579 --> 00:44:42,458
I don't even want to know
their gimmick for that.

605
00:44:43,098 --> 00:44:45,141
My mask is so itchy!

606
00:44:47,602 --> 00:44:48,728
But you know guys...

607
00:44:49,343 --> 00:44:51,011
I like costume parties.

608
00:44:52,163 --> 00:44:53,706
What if they choose
your costume?

609
00:44:54,609 --> 00:44:55,609
Pass!

610
00:45:05,453 --> 00:45:07,747
Good evening, ladies
and gentlemen.

611
00:45:07,833 --> 00:45:09,251
My name is Fritzy.

612
00:45:09,383 --> 00:45:12,169
Your host for the night.

613
00:45:12,587 --> 00:45:15,006
A round of applause please!

614
00:45:18,466 --> 00:45:21,584
So many wonderful outfits
and looks tonight...

615
00:45:21,636 --> 00:45:23,096
I'm so happy!

616
00:45:23,330 --> 00:45:27,302
It's giving mystery glam!

617
00:45:28,351 --> 00:45:29,351
Oh...

618
00:45:29,936 --> 00:45:31,104
I see.

619
00:45:31,354 --> 00:45:34,065
Even with these stylish
outfits provided

620
00:45:34,090 --> 00:45:36,843
the newbies still look ugly.

621
00:45:37,152 --> 00:45:38,360
That’s okay,

622
00:45:38,361 --> 00:45:39,905
you're wearing masks.

623
00:45:40,133 --> 00:45:42,051
No need to be ashamed.

624
00:45:42,949 --> 00:45:44,117
Anyway.

625
00:45:44,993 --> 00:45:46,953
Let's get this party started

626
00:45:47,126 --> 00:45:49,958
by welcoming the guests of honor.

627
00:45:50,114 --> 00:45:53,138
The administration
of Hell University.

628
00:45:53,381 --> 00:45:54,465
First up

629
00:45:54,490 --> 00:45:57,379
the head of the Supreme
Student Government

630
00:45:57,522 --> 00:45:59,107
SSG advisor.

631
00:45:59,132 --> 00:46:01,384
Ms. Katherine Velasquez.

632
00:46:07,182 --> 00:46:08,433
Next stop!

633
00:46:09,184 --> 00:46:11,728
The Vice President
of Hell University.

634
00:46:12,187 --> 00:46:14,606
You know him as the creator
of The Bloody Night

635
00:46:15,941 --> 00:46:18,777
also known as Freedom Night.

636
00:46:19,611 --> 00:46:21,863
Please give a warm welcome

637
00:46:21,973 --> 00:46:24,475
Mr. Francisco Agustin.

638
00:46:28,286 --> 00:46:29,286
It can't be.

639
00:46:30,673 --> 00:46:31,673
What the...

640
00:46:32,415 --> 00:46:34,333
the old man is part of the admin?

641
00:46:34,334 --> 00:46:35,919
That bastard!

642
00:46:36,127 --> 00:46:37,963
Thought he was just a caretaker.

643
00:46:38,546 --> 00:46:40,548
They played us like a fiddle.

644
00:46:40,822 --> 00:46:41,823
Crazy.

645
00:46:41,848 --> 00:46:42,536
Now...

646
00:46:42,561 --> 00:46:43,810
Let me ask you.

647
00:46:44,010 --> 00:46:45,720
Are you ready Hell U?

648
00:46:47,693 --> 00:46:50,083
I said, are you ready!?

649
00:46:53,507 --> 00:46:56,009
Last but definitely not the least,

650
00:46:56,386 --> 00:47:00,575
your favorite and mine,
Madam Violet Rivera!

651
00:47:15,625 --> 00:47:19,671
Thank you for that very
spirited introduction, Fritzy.

652
00:47:20,588 --> 00:47:23,466
I'm overjoyed to see each
and every one of you.

653
00:47:23,925 --> 00:47:25,467
But I won't make this speech long

654
00:47:25,468 --> 00:47:28,138
cause I know you're
all ready to party.

655
00:47:29,889 --> 00:47:31,182
Students...

656
00:47:32,058 --> 00:47:33,727
estemeed guests.

657
00:47:34,936 --> 00:47:36,562
By the power vested in me

658
00:47:36,563 --> 00:47:39,065
as the headmistress of Hell University

659
00:47:39,399 --> 00:47:43,873
I declare that now is the official start

660
00:47:44,020 --> 00:47:47,106
of this year's
acquaintance party.

661
00:47:52,996 --> 00:47:55,348
Please enjoy the night.

662
00:48:16,411 --> 00:48:17,411
Cheers!

663
00:48:17,854 --> 00:48:18,982
Cheers!

664
00:48:24,886 --> 00:48:26,387
Good evening, Ms. Shion.

665
00:48:28,144 --> 00:48:29,354
Vice President,

666
00:48:29,412 --> 00:48:31,205
what pleasure do I owe you?

667
00:48:31,554 --> 00:48:34,223
I haven't congratulated
you formally.

668
00:48:34,489 --> 00:48:35,908
For being the new.

669
00:48:36,103 --> 00:48:39,481
Supreme Student
Government Secretary.

670
00:48:40,151 --> 00:48:42,320
Am I supposed to
be happy about that?

671
00:48:44,166 --> 00:48:47,044
Just give it to the one
that's thirsty for that position.

672
00:48:47,607 --> 00:48:49,651
It's the Supremo's decision,

673
00:48:49,877 --> 00:48:51,462
his orders are absolute.

674
00:48:51,712 --> 00:48:53,631
You have no choice.

675
00:48:54,064 --> 00:48:56,441
I have no choice either.

676
00:48:57,811 --> 00:48:59,270
Be happy, Ms. Shion.

677
00:48:59,295 --> 00:49:02,590
Supremo's really particular
in choosing his secretary.

678
00:49:03,483 --> 00:49:05,485
Because of that position

679
00:49:05,860 --> 00:49:09,656
you quickly climbed to the ninth rank.

680
00:49:10,782 --> 00:49:11,802
What?

681
00:49:13,583 --> 00:49:15,043
I'll take my leave then.

682
00:49:16,237 --> 00:49:17,988
Congrats again, Ms. Shion.

683
00:49:19,334 --> 00:49:20,669
Oh my god!

684
00:49:21,140 --> 00:49:22,683
That's so fast!

685
00:49:22,961 --> 00:49:24,671
Rank nine!?

686
00:49:24,696 --> 00:49:26,614
And the secretary too?

687
00:49:26,769 --> 00:49:29,396
Whatever curse you have,
can I have some of it?

688
00:49:29,868 --> 00:49:31,244
Your luck is overflowing!

689
00:49:31,525 --> 00:49:33,235
You can leave this place, Zein!

690
00:49:34,764 --> 00:49:36,558
And rank nine...

691
00:49:37,225 --> 00:49:39,560
of all the ranks you've received

692
00:49:39,561 --> 00:49:41,646
that's the highest you've achieved.

693
00:49:41,980 --> 00:49:43,355
Congrats, Zein!

694
00:49:43,356 --> 00:49:44,481
That's our girl!

695
00:49:44,482 --> 00:49:45,482
Cheers!

696
00:49:47,193 --> 00:49:48,193
Cheers!

697
00:49:49,237 --> 00:49:50,280
Zein!

698
00:49:56,369 --> 00:49:57,537
Zein...

699
00:49:58,079 --> 00:50:00,123
don't accept that position.

700
00:50:01,166 --> 00:50:03,710
Don't forget, this
is still Hell University.

701
00:50:03,918 --> 00:50:05,837
Everything here has
consequences.

702
00:50:06,087 --> 00:50:07,547
Calm down, Matt.

703
00:50:08,844 --> 00:50:10,971
Let Zein decide for herself.

704
00:50:11,136 --> 00:50:13,263
It's her choice, remember?

705
00:50:14,888 --> 00:50:15,930
Dave's right, Matt.

706
00:50:16,135 --> 00:50:17,375
Let Zein make her own decision.

707
00:50:18,028 --> 00:50:19,947
Let her leave this hell.

708
00:50:20,435 --> 00:50:22,896
And she can get help
from the outside.

709
00:50:26,191 --> 00:50:29,777
Are you going to accept
the position, Zein?

710
00:50:40,830 --> 00:50:42,332
That girl!

711
00:50:43,707 --> 00:50:45,167
I'll think about it.

712
00:50:45,573 --> 00:50:46,573
Excuse me.

713
00:50:46,796 --> 00:50:48,256
Zein!

714
00:51:37,704 --> 00:51:39,123
Is it the promotion?

715
00:51:40,473 --> 00:51:42,267
Bad idea if you ask me.

716
00:51:44,394 --> 00:51:48,189
You have to hold a knife
if you accept that position.

717
00:51:49,440 --> 00:51:51,484
You should've been dead by now

718
00:51:51,609 --> 00:51:53,778
if he wasn't keen on protecting you.

719
00:51:55,697 --> 00:51:59,117
But he can't protect you forever.

720
00:52:01,327 --> 00:52:05,290
Hold the knife, Zein. Before it's too late.

721
00:52:12,403 --> 00:52:13,947
Who are you?

722
00:52:14,205 --> 00:52:15,706
Who are you?

723
00:52:16,501 --> 00:52:19,380
- Answer me!
- Miss, take it easy!

724
00:52:20,820 --> 00:52:22,071
Sorry...

725
00:52:27,926 --> 00:52:29,134
Did you find Zein?

726
00:52:29,174 --> 00:52:30,550
It's too dark outside

727
00:52:30,815 --> 00:52:32,275
and everyone's wearing masks.

728
00:52:32,608 --> 00:52:34,527
I almost got lost.

729
00:52:35,320 --> 00:52:37,529
Matt, this is your fault!

730
00:52:37,530 --> 00:52:39,907
You should've have pressured her.

731
00:52:40,033 --> 00:52:43,828
Aren't you curious why she got
that position so easily?

732
00:52:43,967 --> 00:52:44,635
What?

733
00:52:44,660 --> 00:52:46,287
It's a little too convenient

734
00:52:47,206 --> 00:52:49,098
- don't you think?
- What do you mean?

735
00:52:50,043 --> 00:52:53,546
Why does it seem like you
don't want us to be happy for Zein?

736
00:52:53,571 --> 00:52:56,324
That's not my intentions,
I'm just worried for her!

737
00:53:03,096 --> 00:53:03,764
- Oh my God!
- Dave!

738
00:53:03,789 --> 00:53:04,289
Shit!

739
00:53:04,314 --> 00:53:05,481
- Bro, are you okay?
- Dave!

740
00:53:06,517 --> 00:53:07,852
Shit!

741
00:53:10,701 --> 00:53:13,450
Since when did Dave's tolerance
for alcohol get so low?

742
00:53:14,632 --> 00:53:15,632
Dave...

743
00:53:16,396 --> 00:53:19,297
Shit, let's bring him to the clinic!

744
00:53:19,322 --> 00:53:20,323
Dave, are ou okay?!

745
00:53:20,677 --> 00:53:21,845
Zein...

746
00:53:22,867 --> 00:53:24,160
Zein!

747
00:53:25,363 --> 00:53:28,473
Matt, help me! He's in a bad shape.

748
00:53:29,925 --> 00:53:30,925
Shit!

749
00:53:31,437 --> 00:53:32,692
Where did Matt go?

750
00:53:33,486 --> 00:53:34,111
Where is he?

751
00:53:34,136 --> 00:53:35,178
Zein!

752
00:53:35,270 --> 00:53:37,465
They drank the same thing.

753
00:53:37,560 --> 00:53:38,560
Fuck!

754
00:53:42,470 --> 00:53:44,305
Dave, wake up!

755
00:53:44,362 --> 00:53:45,362
Dave!

756
00:55:13,811 --> 00:55:14,811
Zein?

757
00:55:16,814 --> 00:55:17,814
Zein...

758
00:55:19,734 --> 00:55:20,734
What happened?

759
00:55:21,235 --> 00:55:22,235
Zein?

760
00:55:29,785 --> 00:55:32,872
Help, please!

761
00:55:43,132 --> 00:55:46,092
Their drink was compromised
by an illegal drug.

762
00:55:46,093 --> 00:55:48,762
They drank a high dosage,
that's why they're like this.

763
00:55:48,763 --> 00:55:49,847
Zein...

764
00:55:50,822 --> 00:55:52,783
Can't you see she's
literally dying already!?

765
00:55:52,808 --> 00:55:54,227
Let's wait for the doctor.

766
00:55:54,852 --> 00:55:55,937
Excuse me.

767
00:55:56,222 --> 00:55:57,932
Whoever did this,

768
00:55:58,294 --> 00:56:00,791
I swear I won't forgive him.

769
00:56:00,816 --> 00:56:02,585
She needs to be treated right away

770
00:56:02,610 --> 00:56:04,987
but nobody seems to care
in this goddamn place!

771
00:56:05,012 --> 00:56:09,068
Aren't you happy that there
will be no bloodshed tonight?

772
00:56:10,863 --> 00:56:13,023
What about what happned earlier,
what do you call that?
